    "body": "Not sure if relevant here or it should be its own feature, but it would be very nice if the formatter could:\r\n- Automatically remove testing libraries import statements \r\n- Automatically remove any `emit log`/`console.log` statements\r\n- Automatically remove anything marked by some specific comment statement (like hadolint, shellhint, etc.)\r\n\r\nThe idea being that you code and test freely and then before closing the final PR and deploying, you can format it and know that the final PR will be clean. ",
